By the time those ideas=E2=80=99 productivity was realized, they were relat=
ively old ideas. As Perplexity concluded [ https://substack.com/redirect/93=
84a90a-d186-4dd7-8277-0547c2625f58?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaM=
ZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], =E2=80=9CIn conclusion, while the 1950s and 1=
