ow progress happened. Edison=E2=80=99s electrical wires electrocuted people=
=2E The Wright Brothers faceplanted int=
o the Kitty Hawk sand during test flig=
hts. The boilers on Vanderbilt=E2=80=99s steamships occasionally exploded. =
Then they iterated, improved, even undertook new research to create new and=
 improved ideas to address the obstacles that can only be exposed by intera=
