=2E NASA and the DoD were the premium d=
emand for SpaceX&#8217;s early launch;=
 now, the benefits can be felt by anyone who uses Starlink to access the in=
ternet.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-=
height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">For a certain set of technologies, this =
