=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">Despite the slowdown, technological progress has marched on. Comp=
ared to 1973, entrepreneurs have a cornucopia of lower-cost, higher-perform=
